						<summary>

						<p>On a stone lying in front of Yusuf-sahib's house.</p>						

						<p>Circa 12th century.</p>						

						<p>This commences with an invocation to the Varāha incarnation. It seems to describe an eminent personage. The inscription being badly damaged, its purport cannot be made out. </p>						

